race.comment: MIDNIGHT QUEEN (1) shapes well for this after winning last start over the 520m at Q Parklands in a convincing 29.55. In form and rates on top again. LAKEVIEW EMILY (3) had been super consistent recording two placings in a row before she was rewarded with a win last time, scoring at Sandown over 515m (29.28). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Expected to feature again. FLAT OUT FREDDY (2) could not have been more impressive last start in his a head turning 29.97 win at The Meadows over 525m. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. TRIBECA (6) is a last start winner worth following up.
